<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>About Us</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />
  <style>
    /* Basic Styling */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    /* Header Styling */
    .header {
      background-color: #240750;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Main Content Styling */
    .main-content {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .main-content h1 {
      color: #240750;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .main-content p {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Image Styling */
    .about-image {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    /* Footer Styling */
    .footer {
      background-color: #240750;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-in-out; 
    }

    .footer-content {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .footer-content p {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    /* Animation for Links */
    .footer a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 10px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease; 
    }

    .footer a:hover {
      transform: scale(1.1);
      color: #f1c40f; 
    }

    /* Fade In Up Animation */
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      0% {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    /* Animated Footer Text */
    .footer-animation {
      display: inline-block;
      animation: slideUp 3s infinite ease-in-out;
    }

    @keyframes slideUp {
      0% {
        transform: translateY(0);
        opacity: 1;
      }
      50% {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
        opacity: 0.7;
      }
      100% {
        transform: translateY(0);
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .main-content {
        width: 90%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Include Header -->
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <!-- Main Content Section -->
  <div class="main-content">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>Welcome to [Your Website Name]! We are committed to delivering a seamless user experience with dynamic content and personalized services.</p>

    <!-- Team Image -->
    <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
    <img src="https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/teamwork-concept-landing-page_23-2148191420.jpg?t=st=1727582497~exp=1727586097~hmac=c304964227609ec5f50fdfe733552ba98abfae30b9d5fb950c7900e77b8f8a69&w=826" />
    <p>Our dedicated team of professionals works tirelessly to bring you the best experience. Get to know the faces behind the brand.</p>

    <!-- Service Image -->
    <h2>Our Services</h2>
    <img src="https://img.freepik.com/premium-photo/certification-standards-iso-business-certification-international-standards_1101054-55001.jpg?w=996" alt="Our Services" class="about-image" />
    <p>We offer a wide range of products and services tailored to meet the needs of our diverse clientele. From product A to service B, we've got you covered.</p>

    <h4>Technology Stack</h4>
    <img src="https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/server-room-cloud-data-cloud-storage-big-data-processing-concept-networking-internet_39422-625.jpg?t=st=1727553375~exp=1727556975~hmac=90597973d937ca26d04d8c1c2ba920a441cafd2b7f2159718c2d9e840de133cf&w=1060" alt="">
    <p>We use cutting-edge technology, including Node.js, MongoDB, and React, to ensure a smooth, efficient, and secure user experience.</p>

    <h4>User Guidance</h4>
    <img src="https://img.freepik.com/premium-photo/attracting-retaining-customers-with-your-calling-card_1106493-462852.jpg?w=740" alt="">
    <p>Explore our website to learn more about what we offer. If you have any questions, feel free to reach out through our contact page.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Animated Footer Section -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-content">
      <p>&copy; 2024 [Your Website Name]. All Rights Reserved.</p>
      <p class="footer-animation">
        Follow Us: 
        <a href="#">Facebook</a> | 
        <a href="#">Twitter</a> | 
        <a href="#">Instagram</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
